_-------------- CODE FLOW -----------------------

1] RANDOM NUMBER WILL BE GENERATED  AND STORED IN A FILE
2] THREE  FILE WILL BE GENERATED 
	- FOR ASCENDING ORDER
	- FOR DESCENDING ORDER
	- FOR RANDOM NUMBER

3] INPUT WILL BE TAKEN FROM THESE THREE FILE AND EACH ALGORITHM WILL RUN THEM.

4] SORTED NUMBER WILL BE STORED IN A DIFFERENT THREE FILE.

5] DIFFERENT RUN TIME WILL BE RECORDED FOR DIFFERENT DATA SET SIZE AND A GRAPH WILL BE PLOTTED